Hello,

Enclosed is your December, 15 2022 Fulfillment Partner Payout Statement. Fo=
r better understanding of the statement, please reference the items below:

* *Number of Orders Fulfilled* : The total orders that were fulfilled in th=
e payout period.
* *Delivery Gross Sales from Orders* : Includes all delivered, cancelled, a=
nd unfulfilled orders. Gross sales are not reduced by error adjustments.
* *Pick Up Gross Sales from Orders* : Includes all picked up orders.
* *Gross Sales Tax (Remitted)* : Gross Sales Tax collected on all orders an=
d remitted by the online order systems platforms.
* *Discrepancies on Payouts* : If there are any discrepancies on the semi-m=
onthly payout these will be reflected in your payout at the end of the mont=
h. If any additional discrepancies exist at the end of the month, please co=
ntact your Account Manager.
* *Payout Amount* : The total amount paid out by Nextbite is highlighted in=
 green on your statement.
* *Payout Process* : Payouts are issued on the 5th business day following t=
he 15th and the last day of the month.

If you have not received your payout for the month, please inform your acco=
unt manager as soon as possible.

Please note: Your Ordermark admin dashboard should not be used for accounti=
ng purposes. Ordermark captures order totals when orders come in, but it do=
es not update for any events following the initial order placement (e.g., c=
ancelled, unfulfilled, and refunded). This means the Ordermark dashboard no=
rmally shows order totals greater than the statement data provided by onlin=
e ordering systems delivery apps.

**Do not reply to this email**. Please contact your Account Manager with an=
y questions.
Thank you,

Nextbite Team
