        <br/>
        <p>Hello,<br>
            <br>
            Enclosed is your December, 31 2022 Fulfillment Partner Payout S=
tatement.
            For better understanding of the statement, please reference the=
 items below:<br><br>
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Number of Orders Fulfilled</strong>: The total orde=
rs that were fulfilled in the payout period.</li>
            <li><strong>Delivery Gross Sales from Orders</strong>: Includes=
 all delivered, cancelled, and unfulfilled orders. Gross sales are not redu=
ced by error adjustments.</li>
            <li><strong>Pick Up Gross Sales from Orders</strong>: Includes =
all picked up orders.</li>
            <li><strong>Gross Sales Tax (Remitted)</strong>: Gross Sales Ta=
x collected on all orders and remitted by the online order systems platform=
s.</li>
            <li><strong>Discrepancies on Payouts</strong>: If there are any=
 discrepancies on the semi-monthly payout these will be reflected in your p=
ayout at the end of the month. If any additional discrepancies exist at the=
 end of the month, please contact your Account Manager.</li>
            <li><strong>Payout Amount</strong>: The total amount paid out b=
y Nextbite is highlighted in green on your statement.</li>
            <li><strong>Payout Process</strong>: Payouts are issued on the =
5th business day following the 15th and the last day of the month.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            <span style=3D"color: red">If you have not received your payout=
 for the month, please inform your account manager as soon as possible.</sp=
an><br>
            <br>
            Please note: Your Ordermark admin dashboard should not be used =
for accounting purposes. Ordermark captures order totals when orders come i=
n, but it does not update for any events following the initial order placem=
ent (e.g., cancelled, unfulfilled, and refunded). This means the Ordermark =
dashboard normally shows order totals greater than the statement data provi=
ded by online ordering systems delivery apps.<br>
            <br>
            <strong>*Do not reply to this email*</strong>. Please contact y=
our Account Manager with any questions.<br/>
            Thank you,<br>
            <br>
            Nextbite Team=20
